                     <interp inst="t18480612-1567-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 bag, value 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 30 sovereigns, and 10 half-sovereigns; the property of <persName id="t18480612-name-640" type="victimName">
